      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a rewarding project with this diamond in the rough! While this vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a classic model at a budget-friendly price and truly make it your own. Perfect for someone looking for a parts car or a full-on weekend challenge!",
